00:18:42.317 --> 00:18:47.141
And in that silence, he then chooses to speak.

00:18:47.161 --> 00:18:52.306
And again, I just want you to understand, like this is not Jacob's strategic plan.

00:18:52.346 --> 00:18:56.530
He didn't send everyone away so that he could have silence.

00:18:56.866 --> 00:18:59.869
He could strategize or whatever.

00:18:59.909 --> 00:19:01.571
Maybe he just wanted some sleep.

00:19:01.711 --> 00:19:05.335
Sounds like he had a ton of kids, multiple wives, all this stuff.

00:19:05.355 --> 00:19:10.681
It's like, our kids are seven, five, four and two and our house is busy, they're all boys.

00:19:11.122 --> 00:19:15.447
So it's like wrestling match, yelling, screaming, fighting, all day long.

00:19:15.947 --> 00:19:17.609
I call it a beautiful chaos.

00:19:18.730 --> 00:19:20.512
And maybe he just wanted some sleep.

00:19:21.473 --> 00:19:25.778
Maybe he just wanted some sleep, but he got something very different.

00:19:26.786 --> 00:19:37.081
And what happens next, it's wild to look at because what happens next is this wrestling, not something that Jacob had planned for.

00:19:37.121 --> 00:19:43.169
And it wasn't Jacob who initiated this wrestling match, it was God.

00:19:44.291 --> 00:19:45.973
