00:20:57.958 --> 00:21:03.327
So it's just Jacob in God and sometimes God will do something to get your attention.

00:21:06.852 --> 00:21:07.894
And he wrestles with him.

00:21:08.435 --> 00:21:10.258
And it's,

00:21:10.914 --> 00:21:19.365
It's really interesting in that it's not like there's this wrestling partner, you know, they're not going back and forth.

00:21:20.446 --> 00:21:26.013
I'm from the south, so we would call this a butt whooping, you know, is what Jacob's getting here.

